R14_usr RN      14

R10_fiq RN      10
R11_fiq RN      11
R12_fiq RN      12
R13_fiq RN      13
R14_fiq RN      14

R13_irq RN      13
R14_irq RN      14

R13_svc RN      13
R14_svc RN      14

